  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n\r\nImplement `transferAndCall` ([ERC677](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/677)) on top of ERC20.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n* ERC20 [`transfer`](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/54182bf31c78fb1b16dfdce40fc9a6a177cb3bca/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol#L62) function emits [`Transfer`](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/54182bf31c78fb1b16dfdce40fc9a6a177cb3bca/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol#L160) event with `(sender, recipient, amount)`\r\n* ERC677 `transferAndCall` emits `Transfer` event with `(sender, recipient, amount, data)`.\r\n\r\nIf I'm listening to Transfer events on some oracle I don't have a way to distinguish them.\r\n\r\nIs there planned support for this in the future?\r\n",
